data.description: This is the perfect home for a first time home buyer or investor for rental income. This 3 Bedroom 1.5 bath home is ready for you to call home. Not in a flood zone, large yard, convenient location, architectural shingles, no carpet, newer paint throughout the interior and exterior, newer flooring, newer ceiling fans, newer toilets, newer electrical outlets and switches, newer thermostat, inside and outside AC replaced in 2006 and serviced within the past 30 days. Covered carport with easy access to the eat-in dining room/kitchen. Completely fenced large back yard.
